Cache Hierarchy Decision Tree. Request -> Check Response Cache (Exact Hash Hit?) -> Yes: Return Cached -> No: Check Semantic Cache (Embedding Similarity > 0.92?) -> Yes: Return Similar Cached -> No: Check Prompt Cache (KV-Cache Prefix Hit?) -> Yes: LLM Call with Cached Prefix -> No: Full LLM Call -> Store in Response Cache + Semantic Cache. Annotations: "Response Cache: 100% savings", "Semantic Cache: 20-40% savings", "Prompt Cache: 50-90% prefill savings". Cost savings per level. German labels.